Remediation Recommendations

Whitelist file extensions rather than blacklisting — only allow PDF, DOC, DOCX, ODT, TXT explicitly
Serve uploads through a PHP script that sets correct Content-Disposition headers rather than serving from a web-accessible directory
Protect the review page with strong authentication — not just a shared password
Remove public access to uploads.jsonl — serve it only through authenticated endpoints
Fix the SUID binary to resolve the target path at install time rather than using a runtime-configurable file
Use realpath() checks in the SUID binary to prevent symlink attacks


